          <h2 data-template-id="scenario-title" class="canva-text serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl leading-tight mb-3" style="color: rgb(245, 239, 228); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-size: 24px;">Billing issue recovery</h2>
          <p data-template-id="scenario-description" class="canva-text text-[#aeb9c7] max-w-2xl leading-7" style="color: rgb(174, 185, 199); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Practice a calm, confident response to a frustrated customer who was charged twice for their subscription.</p>
