         <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 text-[#9fe3c7]"><i data-lucide="message-square-heart" class="w-4 h-4"></i> <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.16em] font-semibold">Coach note</span>
         </div>
         <p id="coach-note" class="text-sm leading-6 text-[#c7d1dc]">Your coach will give instant feedback after each response.</p>
