         <h2 data-template-id="skills-title" class="canva-text serif text-2xl" style="color: rgb(245, 239, 228); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-size: 24px;">Skill signals</h2><i data-lucide="list-checks" class="w-5 h-5 text-[#9fe3c7]"></i>
