         </div>
         <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3"><span id="skill-close-icon" class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full border border-white/10 grid place-items-center text-[#7c8b9f]"><i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i></span> <span class="text-sm text-[#d9dfdf]">Close confidently</span>
          </div><span id="skill-close" class="text-xs text-[#7f8fa2]">Pending</span>
         </div>
        </div>
       </section>
      </aside>
     </div>
     <section id="complete-view" class="hidden fade-in">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto glass rounded-[30px] p-7 sm:p-10 text-center">
       <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-[#9fe3c7] text-[#0d1726] grid place-items-center mx-auto mb-6"><i data-lucide="badge-check" class="w-8 h-8"></i>
       </div>
       <p data-template-id="complete-kicker" class="canva-text text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#9fe3c7] font-semibold mb-3" style="color: rgb(159, 227, 199); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.22rem;">Practice complete</p>
       <h2 data-template-id="complete-title" class="canva-text serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-4" style="color: rgb(245, 239, 228); font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-size: 24px;">That call is in the books.</h2>
       <p data-template-id="complete-copy" class="canva-text text-[#b6c2cf] leading-7 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8" style="color: rgb(182, 194, 207); font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;">Review your result, note your strongest skill, and run it again to make the language feel natural.</p>
       <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8 text-left">
